TextEng: I would speak with you... and perhaps more.
Text: 당신과 이야기하고 싶군요... 어쩌면 그 이상도.

TextEng: Me talk with yous? Maybe more?
Goodbye.
<StartAction>Bemoan about how no one really respects you.</Start>
Let's talk about you, and what you like.
You listen well? Does talking make your "clients" more relaxed?
Text: 말을 잘 들어주나요? 손님들이랑 대화하면 더 편안해지던가요?

TextEng: Perhaps I could ask some serious questions?
Text: 진지한 질문을 몇 가지 해도 될까요?

TextEng: We talk about you, handsome kinda guy.
You listen? Talking make customers feel more happy?
Text: 너 들어줘? 말하면 손님들 기분 좋아져?

TextEng: Maybe me ask serious stuffs, okay?
Where are you from? What is your story?
Where you from? What your story?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> I'd find it degrading to disguise my true self like that.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 진짜 자신을 숨기는 건, 내겐 모욕처럼 느껴져.

TextEng: I want to talk about something else.
Me talk about different things.
<StartAction>Lament the inherent loneliness of the adventurer lifestyle.</Start>
Nothing bothers me. I am strong.
Me strong. Nothing hurt me.
Text: 나 쎄. 아무것도 못 아프게 해.

TextEng: Whatever, plaything. I'm not here to talk.
Text: 됐어, 놀이상대야. 수다 떨러 온 게 아니야.

TextEng: Shaddap. Me not here for words, lap-lad.
Text: 닥쳐. 난 말하러 온 거 아냐, 접대 총각.

TextEng: There's more than talking, right?
We not just talk, right?
Here is a Pass Coin. My name is <FirstName>.
Here my Pass Coin. Me called <FirstName>.
I don't have a Pass Coin.
Me not gots Pass Coin.
I should be going.
Me should go, maybe.
I'll stay a while, I think.
Me not so dumb. Me stay.
I must leave. Farewell.
Me gots to go. Bye.
Perhaps we could... retire to your bedchambers?
Maybe we go sleep now? Nicely, I mean.
Forget the talk. Let's wrassle!
Let's make two-butt beast!
What do you know of the plague?
Know anything about plague?
Shouldn't you be ashamed, working here?
You maybe ashamed of working here?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> That's very selfless, giving of yourself like that.
What *I* need? Right. You do this to help others. Ha!
Text: 내가 '필요'해서? 그래요. 남을 돕겠다고 이 일을 한다고요. 하!

TextEng: Me not that stupid! You not here to help!
Text: 나 그렇게 바보 아냐! 너 남 도우려고 있는 거 아냐!

TextEng: Don't make me go upside your head! I've always wanted to say that.
Text: 머리통 한 대 치게 만들지 마! ...이 말 꼭 한번 해보고 싶었거든.

TextEng: <StartAction>Confide that you might have a big role in curing the plague.</Start>
Text: <StartAction>역병 치료에 큰 역할을 맡을지도 모른다고 속내를 털어놓습니다.</Start>

TextEng: I enjoyed our time together. I hope you did as well.
Text: 함께한 시간이 좋았어요. 당신도 그랬길 바랍니다.

TextEng: Me like you. Hope you like me a little.
Text: 나 너 좋아. 너도 나 좀 좋아했음 좋겠어.

TextEng: Just another victim, boy.
Text: 넌 그저 또 하나의 희생자일 뿐이다, 소년.

TextEng: You one of many. Hehe. Me done with you.
Text: 너는 많은 것 중 하나. 헤헤. 너랑은 끝.

TextEng: Just lay with me. That is enough.
Text: 그냥 함께 누워 있어요. 그걸로 충분해요.

TextEng: Maybe we just lay still. That good.
Text: 그냥 같이 누워만 있자. 그거 좋다.

TextEng: Gentle comforts are welcome. I'm not that tired.
Text: 부드러운 위로면 충분해요. 아직 그렇게 피곤하진 않아요.

TextEng: Gentle night, maybe. Me not that tired.
Text: 살살하면 돼. 나 그리 안 피곤해.

TextEng: I'm looking for an animal. Think you can manage?
Text: 난 짐승 같은 상대를 찾고 있어요. 가능하겠습니까?

TextEng: Make me tired. Real tired. Animal man.
Text: 나 지치게 해. 아주 지치게. 짐승 남자.
